ing: 1 (15 ounce) can kidney beans, drained and rinsed
1 (15 ounce) can black beans, rinsed and drained
des: "My husband's Grandmother sent this one to me three times because she liked it so well!  What is great about this soup is that you can add more of one item you really like or make substitutions."
ins: In a large stock pot brown ground beef.  Drain grease and add tomato vegetable juice, tomatoes, kidney beans, black beans, corn and taco seasoning.  Heat through and serve.
